content: 4. Listen up. We know the drill on social media. Don’t agree with someone’s perspective, flame them. Unfriend them. Problem solved, right? Not so fast. Thanks in large part to our online echo chambers, we’ve forgotten how to listen. Even if our politicians can’t figure out how to listen respectfully, we can. We must. Let those you disagree with speak. Listen to what they say. Be prepared to have your own beliefs challenged as you challenge theirs. One friend offers this humorous and effective suggestion: Take off your hearing aids for the day and say, "So sorry, the batteries are dead." Problem solved, at least for her.
